		　Since the position where the button is created is the upper left point of the image specified by the <ref tag="locate">locate</ref> tag, please specify the position with the locate tag before using this tag. This tag does not move the character display position.<BR>
		　The image specified by the graphic attribute is an image in which three images are arranged side by side from the left:<BR>
		・Normal state<BR>
		・Button pressed<BR>
		・The mouse cursor is over the button<BR>
		　In one image, three images of the same size are arranged side by side. In other words, the image specified by this attribute has a width three times the width of the button.<BR>
