				　If you specify true, it will be played repeatedly. If false is specified, it will be played only once. If omitted, it is assumed to be false.<BR>
				　If true is specified, you cannot wait for the end of sound effect playback with the <ref tag="ws">ws</ref> tag.
			</info>
		</attrib>


	</attribs>

	<remarks>
